{
  "text": "RA is a chronic, systemic autoimmune disease of unknown aetiology affecting $1% of the world population. RA is characterized by symmetric polyarthritis associated with pain and swelling in multiple joints that, if left untreated, ultimately leads to joint destruction [CITATION_1] .",
